'''Alexander "Chandler" González''' is the national team manager of the [[Cuba national football team|Cuban national football team]].<ref>{{cite web|title=La selección cubana jugará en Brasil partidos previos a las eliminatorias de la Concacaf|url=http://latino.foxnews.com/latino/sports/2012/05/17/la-seleccion-cubana-jugara-en-brasil-partidos-previos-las-eliminatorias-de-la/|publisher=Fox News|accessdate=22 May 2012|date=17 May 2012}}</ref> He was appointed on April 16, 2012.
He was appointed to the following a spell in charge of the Cuban representative team at the [[Football at the 2011 Pan American Games – Men's tournament|2011 Pan American Games]].
